						 <p>Thank you very much for the prompt removal, it is very much appreciated.</p> <p>Aside from that, I enjoyed this piece very much. +1</p> <p>Edit: <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/estrellayoshte" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3781861&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1601010249" alt="EstrellaYoshte" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3781861)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/estrellayoshte" >EstrellaYoshte</a></span> has informed me that, if you would like, they would be happy to make an Extradimensional Department / Division logo for your purposes. It seems that the Extradimensional aspect was important to your vision of this piece, so I would suggest doing so. You can contact them on wikidot or, more promptly, in the SCPDeclassified Discord.</p> <p>Edit 2<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-339675-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" >1</a></sup>: They've actually created a section on their <a href="http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/desk-of-junior-designer-s-yvonne" target="_blank">authorpage</a> where you can place requests!</p> <div class="footnotes-footer"> <div class="title">Footnotes</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-339675-1"><a href="javascript:;" >1</a>. Electric Boogaloo</div> </div> 
				 	]]>
